I watched the first movie on tv through my computer, but couldn't find the other two.  I play all my favorite Christmas movies every year and knew that I'd want to be able to do the same with this series, especially since dogs are featured.  Now I can easily "retrieve" these movies next Christmas.

Have owned the first movie for years....cute movie, enjoyable even if I had not little children to watch with me.  Caught the 2nd movie on TV during the holidays.  Thought I would purchase the seet and then watch the third movie.  Cute, wholesome movies...

First movie was ok but pretty predictable.  Second movie was less interesting...and I disliked the subplot of the 2 very young kids in a romance.  It was treated like an adult romance and turned me off completely.  I don't know at this point if I'll even bother with the 3rd movie.
